{"tid":1921804,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"暗角欺民以為無人見？ - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-03-12T07:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T07:43:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f41a8136a57980dc6359d2a00b6f60a0d86ffacf","tid":1921804,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200312/20878593/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200312%2F20878593%2F&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=e180046b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200312%2F20878593%2F&h=d37f0d2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200312/20878593/</a><br />\n<br />\n暗角欺民以為無人見？ - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200312/large/1583921886_0a74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200312%2Flarge%2F1583921886_0a74.jpg&h=7014e246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今時今日，此時此刻，若仍有支持黑警欺凌、鎮壓、侮辱、毒打、殺害香港市民者，就是良知泯滅，做警暴幫兇，與黑警一樣，不得好死。<br />\n<br />\n港人都收到網上瘋傳的「七警欺民」片段，這七畜言行令人髮指，明證香港毫無法治可言，且得到包庇縱容，市民憤怒之聲不絕。<br />\n<br />\n日前有市民在將軍澳尚德邨悼念去年11月被墮樓身亡的22歲科大生周梓樂，市民不會忘記冤魂冤獄，一切不公義的傷天害理的惡行。「悼念」是和平活動而已，大批警察在場戒備、濫捕，數十名男女被帶走。<br />\n<br />\n警暴不止，有網媒高處拍到七名（又是「七」？）蒙面、隱證、有裝備沒人性的黑警，包圍一名表明只是路過的市民，不但兇狠以帶威脅性粗言辱罵，更命市民向在場七警逐一道歉，一次不滿意，再逐一道歉，比日本皇軍更橫蠻。帶頭者還大聲斥喝：「破壞法治就係你呢班人呀！」──誰破壞法治？誰欺善怕惡恃強凌弱？<br />\n<br />\n人渣狗吠，暗角欺民，迫害手無寸鐵的市民，滿足自卑感，以為無人見到？但世有天眼，也有疏而不漏的天網，此片令之無所遁形。<br />\n<br />\n黑警自創「新月曆」，999求救召喚不包括7月21日，當然也避忌612、831&hellip;&hellip;月曆也可以改？但一個人的命運和報應改不了，雙手的鮮血也洗不清的。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"693860ba3f54a0e3e5a391c0dcafa6c7192bf5fb","tid":1921804,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:43:59.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾玖期牆紙】 兄弟爬山<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1919455/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1919455/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=b7d2d1ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=73a0d2b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhongkong_wallpaper%2F&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=b0f6c4f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_wallpaper/</a><br />\nWEB: <a href=\"https://firsthand-news.web.app/wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffirsthand-news.web.app%2Fwallpaper%2F&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=c26fa290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://firsthand-news.web.app/wallpaper/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkDtkZf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkDtkZf.jpg&h=0ec8a28f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}